---
title: BBQ Beef Rump and Spicy Sauce with rice and spinach tomato salad
description: If you're looking for something a little lighter—but still packed with flavour— for dinner this week, this could be the dish you've been dreaming of. A BBQ beef rump is accompanied by minty rice and a refreshing tomato salad, with a slightly spicy sriracha sauce on the side—so you can take as much (or as little) as you like!
